reviewText: DVD is in perfect condition as promised.
Nowhere near the quality or energy level as any other Zumba DVD, I am returning it.
Great workout for the days I don't feel like going to the gym. They explain the moves very well. Good purchase and it arrived quickly.

I absolutely Love this workout!!! I lost over 60lbs doing it, and I never got bored. It really did sculpt and tone my body; it also prepared me for a higher level of workout!!! Trust me, you won't be disappointed with this purchase!!!
